{"id":287230,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/04/维权网-11名蒙冤警察反抗暴力截访，赵宏炎受伤入/","date":"2013-04-02T06:31:21Z","modified":"2013-04-02T06:31:21Z","title":"维权网 | 11名蒙冤警察反抗暴力截访，赵宏炎受伤入院（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员疾风报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>日下午</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">40</span><span>分，在北京的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>名蒙冤警察赵宏炎、于立胜、张亚杰、徐兆杰、马治国、雷春凤、谭家卫警察之妻邓朝霞、田兰、黄玲、成龙、刘华琼来到中纪委向纪委领导举报各地政府官员腐败违法情况。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>当赵宏炎走到中纪委门外路边时，一辆辽</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">OA2868</span><span>黑色金杯商务车中忽然跑出四名沈阳市公安局的截访警察将赵宏炎拦截，强行将其推上商务车一阵殴打后，就想开车将赵宏炎带走。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>在现场的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>名蒙冤警察见状，立即冲上前，从车上救下被殴打致脚骨折的赵宏炎。四名沈阳市公安局的截访警察当场丢下车溜之大吉。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>名蒙冤警察赵宏炎、于立胜、张亚杰、徐兆杰、马治国、雷春凤、谭家卫警察之妻邓朝霞、田兰、黄玲、成龙、刘华琼就在四名截访警察丢下的辽</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">OA2868</span><span>黑色金杯商务车旁边合影留，以庆胜利。之后，大家将赵宏炎送入北京展览路医院治疗。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>赵宏炎手机：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13555705095</span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-RZlhcn8F6GE/UVoY47nm0LI/AAAAAAAAfrE/601Zfo-2-0E/s1600/PART_1364807112248.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-RZlhcn8F6GE/UVoY47nm0LI/AAAAAAAAfrE/601Zfo-2-0E/s320/PART_1364807112248.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-QQbT0y74OEU/UVoY7MqTFsI/AAAAAAAAfrM/9TU2jTKNAcY/s1600/DSC_0000128.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-QQbT0y74OEU/UV